WEBVTT

00:04:28.186 --> 00:04:30.072
that can affect your voice.

00:04:30.072 --> 00:04:31.791
But when kept in good condition,

00:04:31.791 --> 00:04:34.596
your voice box 
is a finely tuned instrument,

00:04:34.596 --> 00:04:36.669
capable of operatic arias,

00:04:36.669 --> 00:04:38.091
moody monologues,

00:04:38.091 --> 00:04:39.626
and stirring speeches.